  "description": "<p><strong>1997年，微软以5.03亿美元的价格买下当时名为WebTV的在线机顶盒视频服务，并在2001年改组成MSN TV并一直运营至今。MSN TV采用独立的硬件设备附加到电视来实现内容供应，而16年后的今天，MSN TV宣布将被关闭</strong>，虽然在过去的十几年，MSN TV带来了更为方便的家电访问电视节目的方式，但在视频网站和流媒体服务极为发达的今天，脱胎于Web 1.0的服务早已变得不合时宜。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e4f2ba6/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243777.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C16%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%8B%E4%B9%85%E7%9A%84MSN+TV%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243777.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C16%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%8B%E4%B9%85%E7%9A%84MSN+TV%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243777.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C16%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%8B%E4%B9%85%E7%9A%84MSN+TV%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243777.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C16%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%8B%E4%B9%85%E7%9A%84MSN+TV%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243777.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C16%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%8B%E4%B9%85%E7%9A%84MSN+TV%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1