  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243776.htm", 
  "description": "<p>科技飞速发展的今天，之前很多无法在智能手机上完成的事情都令人惊奇地实现了，而且很多人热爱智能手机超过了自己宠物或男女朋友。<strong>不少用户也早已经将智能手机当做办公的重要工具，因为智能手机能让每个人随时保持联系、查看电子邮件，并且还可以瞬间分享文件和各种“idea”，堪称促进出色完成工作的利 器，以&#160;及最为人们节省时间的重要设备。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e4f2ba5/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243776.htm&amp;t=%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E8%AE%A9%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E6%B5%AA%E8%B4%B9%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243776.htm&amp;t=%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E8%AE%A9%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E6%B5%AA%E8%B4%B9%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243776.htm&amp;t=%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E8%AE%A9%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E6%B5%AA%E8%B4%B9%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243776.htm&amp;t=%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E8%AE%A9%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E6%B5%AA%E8%B4%B9%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww